description: - Textured Black Powder-Coat Finish - Rugged Off Road Styling - Bolt-On Installation - Fit for 2007-2018 Jeep Wrangler JK & Unlimited
JeCar Gas Cover adds an extra level of customization for an aggressive appearance. Not only will this textured black fuel door look great, but it also adds superior protection to your JK.

The JeCar Gas Tank Cover is made of aluminum and crafted with the highest standard ABS plastic, which makes it fully proof against rust. It's also very resistant to corrosion from gasoline and other harsh car-related chemicals, so it can stand up ruggedly to its intended use.
This non-locking fuel door is finger notch opening. Installation does not require any drilling, just easy bolt-on installation using the supplied hardware.

The pinhole position of 2-door JK and 4-door JK is different. The pin guide of our gas cap cover matches 4-door. You may need to knock the pin guide off to install it on a 2-door if you don't wanna drill a new pinhole.
